## Skills & Workflows

**IMPORTANT: Use these skills when the task matches their purpose.**

### Available Skills

| Skill | Trigger Phrases | When to Use |
|-------|-----------------|-------------|
| `site-audit` | "audit site", "review existing" | Before redesigning an existing site |
| `design-system-init` | "set up design", "initialize styles" | Start of any new project |
| `sanity-setup` | "set up Sanity", "configure CMS" | When adding/configuring Sanity |
| `cms-verify` | "verify CMS", "check fields" | Before client handoff |
| `performance-audit` | "check performance", "Lighthouse" | Before launch |
| `design-concepts` | "mockup", "design options" | When creating visual designs |

### Workflow: New Project
```
design-system-init → [build components] → sanity-setup → [add content] → cms-verify → performance-audit
```

### Workflow: Redesign Project
```
site-audit → design-system-init → [build] → sanity-setup → [migrate content] → cms-verify → performance-audit
```

